#+ATTR_HTML: :width 75%
#+CAPTION: Mapping a drive
[[./images2/1-8-mapNetworkDrive.png]]
- Command line - ~net use x: \\[some server]\[some place]~
** Printer sharing vs. network printer mapping
- Can share the computer's local printer with others on the network
- Can map network printer to own machine
** Establish networking connections

*** VPN
- built in VPN client included with windows
- Can integrate different types of ID
  - for multi-factor authentication

#+ATTR_LATEX: :width 0.75\textwidth :placement [h] :float nil
