*** Dial-up
- modem connection over standard phone line
- still possible!
- "Phone and modem" in Control Panel
*** Wireless
#+ATTR_REVEAL: :frag (appear)
- Network name - SSID
- Encryption type:
  - TKIP
  - AES
- WPA2
*** Wired connections
- Ethernet
#+ATTR_LATEX: :width 0.75\textwidth :placement [h] :float nil
#+ATTR_HTML: :width 90%
