*** WWAN (Cellular)
- Wireless Wide Area Network
- built-in mobile technology

** Proxy settings
- Usually set up by larger organizations
- Proxy functions as a go-between:
  - local caching of data increases speed
  - Can restrict network access
** Remote Assistance
- Home editions
- One-time remote access
- Allows one way control by technician to support user
  - Firewall must allow to pass through
** Remote Desktop Connection
#+ATTR_LATEX: :width 0.75\textwidth :placement [h] :float nil
